  26,55,"u nitni, s tidep, sserfan a"
  26,56,"Nekwni, NeqquĂŽa akken ma nella"
  26,57,"Ihi, Nessuffe$ iten id si tebĂȘirin akked tliwa"
  26,58,"igerrujen, ixxamen ukyisen"
  26,59,"Akka, nweĂŽĂŽet yissen, At IsĂŽail"
  26,60,VefĂŽen ten mi d inqeĂŽ yiĂźij
  26,61,"Mi mwalan irebbuyaĂą, nnan imeddukwal n Musa: \"aql a$ a nepwalĂȘeq"
  26,62,"Inna: \"xaĂźi! Mass iw, s tidep, yidi. Ad iyi Inhu"
  26,63,"NweĂȘĂȘa i Musa: \"wwet ill s taĂąkwazt ik\"! ImfaĂŽaq, yal loiha am udrar ameqwĂŽaĂȘan"
  26,64,NessqeĂŽb ed wiyav ar dinna
  26,65,"Nsellek Musa, akked wid akw iddan yides"
  26,66,Sinna ne$ĂŽeq wiyav
  26,67,"Deg wayagi, s tidep, d assekni. Tegwti degsen ur uminen"
  26,68,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, IpĂȘunu"
  26,69,EĂȘku yasen d tamacahup n IbĂŽahim
  26,70,"Mi inna i baba s akked ugdud is: \"d acu tĂąabdem"
  26,71,"Nnan: \"naĂąbed tiĂąancuĂŽin, mazal a tent njjem"
