  26,89,"siwa win iqublen Ăebbi, s wul unĂ»iĂȘ"
  26,90,"A d teppaĂ© Loennet, ar wid ipĂȘezziben"
  26,91,A d innunnet ujajiĂȘ ar im$eĂŽĂŽqen
  26,92,"Ad asen inin: \"anda ten wid tellam tĂąabdem"
