  26,102,"Lemmer ad as nales, a nili d lmumnin"
  26,103,"Deg wayagi, s tidep, assekni. Tegwti, degsen, ur uminen"
  26,104,"Mass ik, s tidep, Neppa, d Uzmir, IpĂȘunu"
  26,105,Agdud n NuĂȘ iskaddeb imazanen
  26,106,"Mi sen inna gmat sen NuĂȘ: \"day ur tepĂȘezzibem ara"
  26,107,"Nek, $uĂŽwen, d amazan muman"
  26,108,"Ihi, ĂȘezzbet i Ăebbi, ta$em iyi awal"
  26,109,"Ur awen ssutre$ kra n teqdiĂąt, ilmend n waya. Ih, taqdiĂąt iw, apan kan, ar Mass imavalen"
  26,110,"Ihi, ĂȘezzbet i Ăebbi, ta$em iyi awal"